<i>noun</i>: 백혈병 [배켤뼝] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>백혈병 [배켤뼝]</dt><br>
<dd>leukemia</dd><br>
<dd>정상적인 백혈구가 적어지고 비정상적인 백혈구가 많아져 고열이나 빈혈, 출혈 등을 일으키는 병.</dd><br>
<dd>A disease that leads to high fever, anemia, blooding, etc. due to the decrease of normal white blood cells along with the increase of abnormal ones.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>